{"tid":1661711,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何君堯直指陳淑莊「個腦有病」引起民主派不滿 及後自行離場","createTime":"2019-10-18T09:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T10:35:18.000Z","uid":212626,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a9dac5400748479a19fc0cf1f7fcbfa065b21196","tid":1661711,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:21:16.000Z","msg":"（獨媒特約報導）立法會內務委員會今早舉行特別會議，繼續選舉主席程序。何君堯繼上週內務委員會再「發功」，指公民黨陳淑莊「個腦有病」，主持郭榮鏗警告何，何自行步離會議室。<br />\n<br />\n陳健波發言時，<span style=\"color: red;\">以「反對派」或「所謂民主派議員」稱呼民主派</span>，毛孟靜不滿，郭榮鏗則促他作為財委會主席，需特別注意言辭。郭則重申他容許議員就立法會保安及管理等事宜發言，是因為內務委員會主席是行政管理委員會當然成員，故今日選舉是同時選舉兩個職位，非常重要。<br />\n<br />\n接著陳淑莊指蔣麗芸不斷重覆<span style=\"color: red;\">「厚顏無恥」</span>四字，而該四字於2004年已被裁定是冒犯性的字眼。她又提到何君堯上週侮辱毛孟靜時，民主派在會議態外接受傳媒訪問時，電視台特別提醒他們不能重覆該些字眼，因為不能「出街」。何君堯要求陳說清楚對他的指控，陳則指「如果上星期咁快忘記，就唔洗係facebook澄清咁耐啦！」表明不會重覆該些字眼。<span style=\"color: red;\">何指陳淑莊「你個腦有病喎，大佬！」郭榮鏗截停其發言，詢問何指誰人有病，何君堯回應稱是陳淑莊，「佢個腦有疾病。」</span>郭警告何君堯，「唔好係度侮辱其他同事話佢個腦有病，話人腦有病係好嚴重既指控。」<span style=\"color: red;\">何君堯自行步離會議室</span>。<br />\n<br />\n郭宣布休會20分鐘觀看重播片段，處理范國威與蔣麗芸的爭議。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1068019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1068019&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz5Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=83e942c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1068019&h=513e01e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1068019</a>"},{"pid":"67e20eea54f15414ee5687c0c1c29440b24e0a3d","tid":1661711,"uid":57513,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:26:19.000Z","msg":"其實呢，當何妖話你正常，你先係個腦有病。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ef04d253c4e744772e32f098978bb2fa69b927","tid":1661711,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:27:01.000Z","msg":"【FC】西九站遊行係中共真春袋！<span style=\"color: red;\">需要針對強國文宣<strong>輸出革命</strong></span>！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1661232\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1661232</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>消息人士表示，7月7日過10萬人去到高鐵西九龍站後，「中國國家安全委員會」就對西九龍站「突發」事件設定了「專案」，就各種事況的發生計劃了處理辦法。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n輸出革命文宣圖：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/akqjfDV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/akqjfDV</a><br />\n<br />\n呢度仲有一單近期爆出嘅關於中共高層貪污嘅核彈新聞，直刺中共心臟，希望都可以唸辦法向強國人宣傳一下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/mDLryDX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/mDLryDX</a>"},{"pid":"f604c4d879b47e2d1521f407e3f03924486b74d8","tid":1661711,"uid":29982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:27:14.000Z","msg":"佢幾時會被皇天擊殺"},{"pid":"5542078b7a3eda7c54edad651b2101b3e19f49d8","tid":1661711,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:27:58.000Z","msg":"殘疾歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6418a988416e26562d1593ddf792327313830d36","tid":1661711,"uid":219564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:28:36.000Z","msg":"佢幾時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126387b1ed4be897a1ace496432022ac890e018f","tid":1661711,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:28:39.000Z","msg":"離場做乜鳩"},{"pid":"85b87164daeacae189adc8ed3aeebc9e3e973b8e","tid":1661711,"uid":233651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67e20eea54f15414ee5687c0c1c29440b24e0a3d","tid":1661711,"uid":57513,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:26:19.000Z","msg":"其實呢，當何妖話你正常，你先係個腦有病。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/nor